qas.question: How many lumens per watt does a typical 100-watt, 120-volt lamp produce?

answers.text: Lower voltage lamps have a thicker filament

qas.question: What is the effect of a thicker filament on bulb temperature?

answers.text: They can run hotter for the same lifetime before the filament evaporates.
